The Redis™ database engine versions available at Scaleway for your clusters.

USAGE:
  scw redis version <command>

AVAILABLE COMMANDS:
  list          List available Redis™ versions
  list-settings List available settings from a Redis™ version

FLAGS:
  -h, --help                help for version
      --list-sub-commands   List all subcommands

GLOBAL FLAGS:
  -c, --config string    The path to the config file
  -D, --debug            Enable debug mode
  -o, --output string    Output format: json or human, see 'scw help output' for more info (default "human")
  -p, --profile string   The config profile to use

Use "scw redis version [command] --help" for more information about a command.
